text: William Bonsall (December 31, 1923 - February 23, 2015) was an American gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:2015 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Philadelphia
